OL,5,G1858 This is BBC Four
OL,6,G1900 University Challenge
OL,7,     F35/37. The semi-finals of the
OL,8,     Ftournament begin. The first of the
OL,9,     Ffour remaining teams do battle for
OL,10,     Fa place in the series final.
OL,11,     FJeremy Paxman asks the questions.
OL,12,G1930 Only Connect
OL,13,     F12/15. Quiz show in which
OL,14,     Fconnections must be made between
OL,15,     Fseemingly random subjects. Three
OL,16,     Fgamblers take on a team unified by
OL,17,     Ftheir love of ten-pin bowling.
